extends layouts/h5bp.jade

block title
  title Patients 

block content
  .patients-top-call-to-action.half-section-padding.hero-font
    .container
      .row
        h1 NephroNet
        h2 We help patients like you navigate the complexities of participating in a clinical trial.
  .woman-doctor.section-padding
    .container
      .row
        .six.columns
          h2.uppercase
  .container.collaborate.half-section-padding
    .row
      .six.columns.uppercase
        h2 My doctor has told me I have kidney disease. What should I do?
      .six.columns
        p There are many factors that cause kidney disease. Talk with your doctor to understanding fully what kind of kidney disease you have. Understanding all your options will help guide you to what is right for you.
  .library
    .container
      .row
        .six.columns.download
          h3 Should I enroll in clinical trial?
          p Understanding your options is the biggest hurdle. Once you know how your kidney disease is treated, deciding if you should enroll in a clinical trial will be easier.
  .container.collaborate.half-section-padding
    .row
      .six.columns.uppercase
        h2 Will a clinical trial help me?
      .six.columns
        p Treatment with investigational new drugs may or may not help you. Participating in clinical trials does bring new information that may be helpful for the treatment of chronic kidney disease
  .social-proof.section-padding
    .container
      .row.uppercase.centered
        h2 Check out these patient resources
        h3 Clinical Trial Info Too!
        a(href='http://www.aakp.org') American Association of Kidney Patients 
        br
        a(href='http://www.kidney.org/patients') American Kidney Foundation 
        br
        a(href='http://www.nephcure.org') Nephcure Kidney International
        br
        a(href='http://www.rsnhope.org') Renal Support Network 
        br
        a(href='http://www.clinicaltrials.gov') Clinical Trials
        br
        a(href='http://www.centerwatch.com') Center Watch 
  .bottom-call-to-action.section-padding
    .container.centered
      .row
        h2 How can we help you?
      .row
        h5 If you decide you want to know more about investigational treatment options let us know. We can help connect you with a clinic close to where you live.
